Requirements
============

1) Google Web Started Kit for responsive web pages

2) Django for MVC architecture

	-> django-cassandra-engine to bridge django with Cassandra

3) Cassandra for data store

4) Apache Lucene for indexing questions



Database Scheme
===============

Users:
	UserId			UUID
	UserName
	FirstName
	LastName
	Email
	Phone
	Rating
	PRIMARYKEY (UserId)


UserTests:
	UserId						UUID
	TestId						UUID
	UserName
	TestName
	RetroRating
	CompanyId
	PositionId
	CompanyName
	PositionName
	State											(0 -> Not Begun, 1 -> In process, 2-> Completed)
	TotalQuestions
	QuestionsAnswered
	CurrentQuestion
	isEvaluated
	TotalMarks
	ScoredMarks
	Q<i>QuestionId
	Q<i>Type
	Q<i>Question
	Q<i>Input
	Q<i>Options
	Q<i>GivenAnswer
	Q<i>ActualAnswer
	Q<i>GivenMark
	Q<i>TotalMark
	PRIMARYKEY (UserId, TestId)

UserCompany:
	UserId
	CompanyId
	CompanyName
	TotalTests
	Position<i>Id
	Position<i>Name
	Test<i>Id
	Test<i>Name
	PRIMARYKEY (UserId, CompanyId)

UserPosition:
	UserId
	PositionId
	PositionName
	TotalTests
	Company<i>Id
	Company<i>Name
	Test<i>Id
	Test<i>Name
	PRIMARYKEY (UserId, PositionId)
	
CompanyPosition
	CompanyId
	CompanyName
	TotalPositions
	Position<i>Id
	Position<i>Name
	PRIMARY KEY (CompanyId)

PositionCompany
	PositionId
	PositionName
	TotalCompanies
	Company<i>Id
	Company<i>Name
	PRIMARY KEY (PositionId)

QuestionBank
	CompanyId
	CompanyName
	PositionId
	PositionName
	QuestionId
	QuestionType
	Question
	Choices
	Answer
	Input
	Rating
	Difficulty
	PRIMARYKEY ((CompanyId,PositionId), Rating)



	
